Package: fitcoach
Type: Package
Title: Personalized Coach for Fitbit
Version: 1.0
Author: Niraj Juneja [aut, cre], Charles de L [aut, cre]
Maintainer:  Niraj Juneja <njuneja@gmail.com>
Description: Improve your Fitbit performance by analyzing your data obtained via fitbit API calls, and by giving personalized recommendations for the rest of the day based on your behavior.
